Project Structure
=================

Root Files:
  config.py          - Central configuration
  orchestrator.py    - Main orchestration engine

Core Packages:
  core/              - Core utilities
    ├── error_handler.py      - Error classification & handling
    ├── input_validator.py    - Input validation & sanitization
    ├── logger.py             - Logging wrapper (backwards compat)
    └── logging_config.py     - Enhanced logging system

  connectors/        - Agent connectors
    ├── base_agent.py         - Base agent interface
    ├── slack_agent.py        - Slack integration
    ├── jira_agent.py         - Jira integration
    ├── github_agent.py       - GitHub integration
    ├── notion_agent.py       - Notion integration
    ├── browser_agent.py      - Browser automation
    ├── scraper_agent.py      - Web scraping
    └── code_reviewer_agent.py - Code review

  orchestration/     - Orchestration system
    ├── action_model.py       - Action data models
    ├── action_parser.py      - Parse actions from LLM
    ├── action_enricher.py    - Enrich actions with context
    └── confirmation_queue.py - Confirmation management

  intelligence/      - AI intelligence components
    ├── intent_classifier.py  - Intent classification
    ├── entity_extractor.py   - Entity extraction
    ├── task_decomposer.py    - Task decomposition
    └── context_manager.py    - Context management

  llms/              - LLM abstraction layer
    ├── base_llm.py           - Base LLM interface
    └── gemini_flash.py       - Gemini implementation

  ui/                - User interface
    ├── terminal_ui.py        - Terminal UI components
    └── confirmation_ui.py    - Confirmation interface

  scripts/           - Utility scripts
    └── migrate_logging.py    - Logging migration tool

  data/              - Data storage
    └── workspace_knowledge.json - Persistent knowledge

  logs/              - Log files (gitignored)
